Crowdedness at the Campus Gym

Justin Dong, David Pham

1/22/2022

About Our Data

Our data set, “Crowdedness at the Campus Gym,” contains 62184 observations total with 11 variables that were measured about different traffic levels at the Berkeley campus gym. The most amount of people inside the gym is 145 while the average amount of people present at the gym is 29.0725428. The average temperature of the location of the gym is 58.5571079, which is much higher than Seattles.
